# Prerequisites

- You're on a Mac
- You have administrative rights on your machine
- You have an App Store account

---

# Upgrade to the latest macOS

- You can get [macOS Sierra from the App Store](https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/macos-sierra/id1127487414?mt=12) for free

---

# Install the latest XCode

- You can get [XCode from the App Store](https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/xcode/id497799835) for free
- Many development tools rely on having XCode installed

