# Start Apps Quickly

- Hold down the Command key (⌘) and press the space bar
- The `Spotlight Search` window pops up
- Type the name of application you want to start, for example `Terminal`
- Press enter
- This is much faster than using the Dock or Finder

---

# Switch Apps Quickly

- Hold down the Command key (⌘) and tap the Tab key repeatedly
- This will take you through your open Apps
- When you let go of the Command key you'll switch to the selected app
- You can hold down Shift to go backwards

---

# Quit Apps Quickly

- Switch back to Terminal
- Hold down the Command key (⌘) and press `Q`

